# Backend the desktop (Tauri) app talks to — it loads the UI locally, so it needs
# an absolute URL. HTTPS Tailscale URL (via `tailscale serve --bg 8000`) — required
# for web push and avoids cleartext issues. Backend currently runs on this PC
# (igorc-1); when it moves to the NAS, run `tailscale serve` there instead.
VITE_API_BASE=https://igorc-1.tailac7b3.ts.net
